NAME
    Date::Japanese::Holiday - Calculate Japanese Holiday.

SYNOPSIS
      use Date::Japanese::Holiday;

      if(Date::Japanese::Holiday->new(2002, 2, 11)->is_holiday) {
           # ...
      }

DESCRIPTION
    Date::Japanese::Holiday calculates Japanese Holiday. this module
    supports from 1948-04-20 to now.

    is_holiday method return true value when the day is Holiday. the Holiday
    does not Include Sunday, Change Holiday.

